      <title>美联储降息提振市场人气，美国股指期货上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/stocks-bonds-rangebound-as-traders-digest-fed-cut-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储将利率下调半个百分点并暗示未来几个月将进一步放松政策后，日本股市与美国股指期货一同上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/stocks-bonds-rangebound-as-traders-digest-fed-cut-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 22:50:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元走弱，投资者等待日本央行政策，日本股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/japan-s-stock-futures-rise-as-yen-pares-gain-traders-await-boj</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔警告不要认为美联储将继续大幅降息，日本股市上涨，日元走弱。投资者正在等待日本央行周五的决定。]]></description>
